attributionInfo.brokerName: CAVINESS & CATES COMMUNITIES BUILDERS MKTG. GROUP

data.description: This Beautiful and spacious home features so many custom touches. The foyer has custom molding & hooks for your coats, formal dining with coffered ceiling, spacious kitchen with granite & tile plus a pantry, family room is open to breakfast bar and leads outside to the covered porch & oversized patio with space for a fire pit ready for entertaining. Upstairs has 3 bedrooms each with its own flare plus a loft area. Don't miss the 2 car garage with work bench or the shed for extra storage. Subdivision name is Roslin Farm West.
